          "value": "At the international level, Eurostat drafts a European regulation for health surveys, which requires member states to conduct a survey including a common set of questions (ECHIS, \"European Core Health Interview Survey\"). The Handicap-Health survey questionnaire takes into account the wording established by Eurostat for the questions concerned."
